metadata.name: FIRST GAME
metadata.description:
And now you're done playing for the first time, you need to put on your sneakers and run to school, but your legs do not obey you from the habit, you are literally exhausted. You want to just sit on the floor and not get up. It looks like today is going to be an unusual day.

-Based on a life story.

Created May 2022 
 
3480x4488 px
